arStrings.szText: While at  maximum stacks of the {c_important}Momentum{/c} Key Passive, your {c_important}Cutthroat{/c} Skills deal {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%|]{/c} increased damage and you become {c_important}{u}Unstoppable{/u}{/c} for {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 2"]{/c} seconds every {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 1"]{/c} seconds.
At maximum stacks of {c_important}Momentum{/c},  you deal increased {c_important}Cutthroat{/c} Skill damage and periodically become {c_important}{u}Unstoppable{/u}{/c}.
